{"tid":1360820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"•••• 破解催淚彈, 其實可唔可以用膠袋？••••","createTime":"2019-07-24T12:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T15:30:57.000Z","uid":287214,"like":0,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6627cb50e5fb75df6218a135c91fd62b08e1fc73","tid":1360820,"uid":287214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:34:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">前線嘅巴絲，可否俾啲意見？ </span></strong></span><br />\n（利申：身在外地）<br />\n<br />\n我成日想試吓，如果一人袋一個膠袋響褲袋，當催淚彈射到附近, 當啲煙未吹到出嚟嘅時候，可否即刻衝埋去用一個膠袋大力紮實佢(如有需要笠佢兩個） ？ <br />\n<br />\n我知道大家嘗試用水或者茶去淋熄佢，但係又要帶水支水又重又嘥野，袋個膠袋會唔會方便啲？ <br />\n<br />\n水可以留返飲呀嘛！同埋洗眼都得！<br />\n<br />\n有冇意見？</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aefebba0d03e0b14fe333e10f9c6362c3db5ab0","tid":1360820,"uid":31237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:35:21.000Z","msg":"好熱"},{"pid":"4b0c107d1734426b49efe3fd119f20b6f355b377","tid":1360820,"uid":46408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:35:23.000Z","msg":"高熱"},{"pid":"a3b99ae7f7bdf437845490c08af11155408c5f12","tid":1360820,"uid":275901,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:35:28.000Z","msg":"熱都熱熔你個膠袋"},{"pid":"39a22e62846319051b6957820f4fa33b46f6b48e","tid":1360820,"uid":288356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:35:32.000Z","msg":"膠袋即溶 完。"},{"pid":"7852d17c181c59aad96fbc7483c3e93b31fbc297","tid":1360820,"uid":147952,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:35:46.000Z","msg":"你知唔知催淚彈好高温 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43282847fa51b36be18e01ba8203ea75e58ed54d","tid":1360820,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:36:09.000Z","msg":"會熔"},{"pid":"4cfb39ed5f8ca34ae9c2c14cae73bba62c7afed5","tid":1360820,"uid":70403,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:36:23.000Z","msg":"有心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫手做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849c518efefd19aa08d0fc24f0359f27198daa98","tid":1360820,"uid":275865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:36:59.000Z","msg":"作用應該唔大，先唔講個袋可能會融，會漏氣，唔漏漲晒又會爆"},{"pid":"f1e14316f5d32c135bda9b836da1b2d94f4a8ccf","tid":1360820,"uid":287214,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:37:30.000Z","msg":"原來是這樣，謝謝大家"},{"pid":"f62ce4a97f31f295724dfec840198cd7080d0446","tid":1360820,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:37:41.000Z","msg":"催淚彈本身發熱，可能2個膠袋都會熱穿吧？<br />\n求高手指教"},{"pid":"09673e31f2bd108e19fa4032650d22bc3c99712c","tid":1360820,"uid":273466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:38:10.000Z","msg":"咁用紙袋？厚身，袋入去，淋水。<br />\n<br />\n可行嗎？"},{"pid":"b4935d9e19c49e06c8d7515ae3c0e56f1d7a2bd6","tid":1360820,"uid":186187,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:39:07.000Z","msg":"未上過前線唔該都做吓資料搜集<br />\n催淚彈燃燒時會發出大量高溫，膠袋？溶撚咗十世，仲要釋放毒氣，加埋啲催淚煙，你想謀害前線勇士？<br />\n無腦P牌，麻煩大家負皮都唔使畀直接上一頁。"},{"pid":"74316a26448296212af22e61301ef84a8d4612e9","tid":1360820,"uid":273466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:39:17.000Z","msg":"一人一個月餅罐？<br />\n蛋卷罐？"},{"pid":"4a72abce73cd6e0e6503e1fea789f61bb87b3383","tid":1360820,"uid":82229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"。。。。。"},{"pid":"7cef7f4abf1151aa328658fc5e5cd9a6a597f4b5","tid":1360820,"uid":280385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:39:50.000Z","msg":"泡沫式手提滅火筒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3808e639554cf7a2d39e2f4c36d9a464e7333ec4","tid":1360820,"uid":287214,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4935d9e19c49e06c8d7515ae3c0e56f1d7a2bd6","tid":1360820,"uid":186187,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:39:07.000Z","msg":"未上過前線唔該都做吓資料搜集<br />\n催淚彈燃燒時會發出大量高溫，膠袋？溶撚咗十世，仲要釋放毒氣，加埋啲催淚煙，你想謀害前線勇士？<br />\n無腦P牌，麻煩大家負皮都唔使畀直接上一頁。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:40:20.000Z","msg":"Brainstorm 下啫"},{"pid":"898c71613e401263f843a95fb368496cb0958006","tid":1360820,"uid":260328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"74316a26448296212af22e61301ef84a8d4612e9","tid":1360820,"uid":273466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:39:17.000Z","msg":"一人一個月餅罐？<br />\n蛋卷罐？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:41:42.000Z","msg":"咁大盒 好難攞"},{"pid":"c597e90def826ded45f438161109897d600675c9","tid":1360820,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:42:18.000Z","msg":"膠袋一定燒穿，用水會更有效果"},{"pid":"3d0e539566b3ba583e6f63694588b2d7f5a66d71","tid":1360820,"uid":287214,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c597e90def826ded45f438161109897d600675c9","tid":1360820,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:42:18.000Z","msg":"膠袋一定燒穿，用水會更有效果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:43:32.000Z","msg":"原來是這樣明白，多謝解答"},{"pid":"cf0b64688b5b0ca9ec3eb01c9fce5189d8012569","tid":1360820,"uid":273466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3808e639554cf7a2d39e2f4c36d9a464e7333ec4","tid":1360820,"uid":287214,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b4935d9e19c49e06c8d7515ae3c0e56f1d7a2bd6","tid":1360820,"uid":186187,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:39:07.000Z","msg":"未上過前線唔該都做吓資料搜集<br />\n催淚彈燃燒時會發出大量高溫，膠袋？溶撚咗十世，仲要釋放毒氣，加埋啲催淚煙，你想謀害前線勇士？<br />\n無腦P牌，麻煩大家負皮都唔使畀直接上一頁。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:40:20.000Z","msg":"Brainstorm 下啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:05:18.000Z","msg":"冇錯，知自己唔聰明，所以先上嚟，希望獲得多啲人討論"},{"pid":"ef9d1ecee82f0ea7c69b949c357f23070d8ca3c8","tid":1360820,"uid":273466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:10:58.000Z","msg":"催淚滅煙 實用手冊大全<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1246199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1246199</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nDaniel_Levy &bull; 6-20<br />\n直接介紹, 催淚彈 612 夢見到既, 有大中細三個SIZE<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n細(1-2cm):<br />\n每一次散10粒左右. <br />\n範圍大, 散煙長度30秒內<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n解決方法:<br />\n <br />\n近距離啪支水落去 (唔好鳩倒)<br />\n<br />\n放入水樽，關蓋。<br />\n<br />\n放入水桶，浸入水，關蓋。<br />\n <br />\n掉入坑渠, 完。<br />\n因為好快散哂D煙，所以掉返過去無用。<br />\n<br />\n中(4-5cm):<br />\n每一次散5粒左右. <br />\n範圍中, 散煙長度1-2分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n解決方法:<br />\n <br />\n近距離啪支水落去 (唔好鳩倒)<br />\n<br />\n放入水桶，浸入水，關蓋。<br />\n <br />\n掉入坑渠, 完。<br />\n <br />\n掉去死角位 (雖然怒火會叫你掉返過去, 不過睇風向掉去大廈死角位)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n示範<br />\n<br />\n大(水樽SIZE):<br />\n每一次1粒. <br />\n目標細, 不過散煙量多, 好幾分鐘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n解決方法:<br />\n <br />\n放入雪糕筒, 雪糕筒頂倒插水樽, 倒插幾支...<br />\n所以一個人就夠, 行過就比支水個個人, 有排搞.<br />\n <br />\n唔好用頭盔，D煙其實都吹到出黎<br />\n <br />\n掉去死角位 (雖然怒火會叫你掉返過去, 不過睇風向掉去大廈死角位)<br />\n<br />\n講多一次，催淚彈都可以攞命。所以要齊裝備先可以做滅煙隊<br />\n眼罩 MUST, 口罩MUST, 勞工手套MUST (有D熱, 會辣手, 不過帶勞工手套係OK的)<br />\n頭盔, 保鮮紙 次要<br />\n<br />\n滅煙隊，其實唔係企最前個D, <br />\n反而企後面兩旁，有個闊D既視野，要冷靜，睇清楚射出黎既目標, <br />\n反應要快, 係後面衝過去滅煙。<br />\n防守為主, 守到既就叫後面上返黎。<br />\n因為每次射完催淚彈，人群入面一定有人嗌向一邊走。 (個個好可疑)<br />\n所以滅煙隊防到既，指揮返D人企返位。<br />\n以狗既其他武器，快避。<br />\n祝大家發個好夢。防守成功。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 所有野都係發夢FF出黎。"},{"pid":"47de6e251b0e6a3a69215fb4c888e22b70abcf9f","tid":1360820,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:11:40.000Z","msg":"後備頭盔"},{"p